app.use((err, _req, res, _next) => {
  req.log?.error(err);
  res.status(err.status || 500).json({ error: 'internal_error' });
});

const port = Number(process.env.PORT) || 3000;
app.listen(port);
module.exports = app;
```

## Priority order
1. **#3** (unauth PII exposure) — fix first.
2. **#1, #2, #7** (helmet, rate limit, error handler) — one-line wins.
3. **#4** (validation scaffolding) — put it in before the next route is added.
