**Severity: Medium**

Express sends no security headers by default (no `Content-Security-Policy`, `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `Referrer-Policy`, etc.). It also advertises itself via `X-Powered-By: Express`, which aids fingerprinting.

