### 8. Listens on all interfaces implicitly (OWASP A05)
`app.listen(3000, ...)` binds to `0.0.0.0`. In container/Kubernetes contexts that is usually intended; in a dev laptop or multi-tenant host it is not. Be explicit:
```js
